240/MjE2MDU5MTg1MzI5MDg4MDE5/shop-good-store-1.jpg 1240w, https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_1400/MjE2MDU5MTg1MzI5MDg4MDE5/shop-good-store-1.jpg 1400w, https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_1720/MjE2MDU5MTg1MzI5MDg4MDE5/shop-good-store-1.jpg 1720w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"shop good store 1\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/t_share/MjE2MDU5MTg1MzI5MDg4MDE5/shop-good-store-1.jpg\" data-src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_860/MjE2MDU5MTg1MzI5MDg4MDE5/shop-good-store-1.jpg\" height=\"2000\" width=\"3000\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePhoto: Courtesy of Shop Good\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe customer: \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eWellness-Driven Beauty Enthusiast: Values \u0026#34;clean,\u0026#34; non-toxic formulations and seeks products that deliver real, skin-improving results.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eHolistic Lifestyle Adopter: Invests in both internal health (nutrition, supplements, self-care rituals) and external care (facials, body treatments).\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eInformed \u0026amp; Curious: Researches ingredients, brand ethics and sustainability; appreciates educational events, one-on-one consultations and community masterclasses. \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eMid-20s to Mid-50s Professional: Typically urban or suburban, with disposable income to spend on premium beauty and wellness experiences.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eEco- and Socially-Conscious Shopper: Prefers brands with transparent sourcing, refill programs, and environmentally responsible packaging.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eCommunity Seeker: Craves connection — whether through membership perks, pop-ups or in-store events — to feel part of a like-minded, wellness-focused group.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSpecial Services:\u003c/strong\u003e Masterclasses with founders; immersive weekend pop-ups; self-care rituals guided by experts; membership program offering exclusive benefits like priority booking, member-only events and curated product drops.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIn stock: \u003c/strong\u003eCosmetics, \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/skin-care\"\u003eskin care\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/hair-care\"\u003ehair care\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/fragrance\"\u003efragrance\u003c/a\u003e and wellness products by brands like Ilia Beauty, Kosas, Osea Malibu, Indie Lee, Marie Veronique and Therabody.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to get in touch: \u003c/strong\u003edreamteam@shop-good.co (\u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/fashion-careers\"\u003ejobs\u003c/a\u003e), hello@shop-good.co (business)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eWant your store featured? Hit the link below.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/page/retailer-store-form\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" phx-track-id=\"image-click\"\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-width: 200px) 200px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_200/MjEwMzI0Mjg4OTA4MDQzODU0/retail-form.webp 200w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 200px) 200px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_200/MjEwMzI0Mjg4OTA4MDQzODU0/r